mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label: Base DPS Formula: ( Base_Damage_Min + Base_Damage_Max + Flat_Physical_Min + Flat_Physical_Max ) / 2 * ( 1 + ( Increased_Physical_Damage_% + Weapon_Quality_% ) / 100 ) * Base_Attack_Speed * ( 1 + Increased_Attack_Speed_% / 100 )
mxTextCell.prevLabel: Base DPS Formula: ( Base_Damage_Min + Base_Damage_Max + Flat_Physical_Min + Flat_Physical_Max ) / 2 * ( 1 + ( Increased_Physical_Damage_% + Weapon_Quality_% ) / 100 ) * Base_Attack_Speed * ( 1 + Increased_Attack_Speed_% / 100 )

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label: Net DPS Formula = Base_DPS * ( Base_Critical_Strike_Chance * ( 1 + Increased_Critical_Strike_Chance )  * ( 0.5 + Increased_Critical_Strike_Multiplier ) )
mxTextCell.prevLabel: Net DPS Formula = Base_DPS * ( Base_Critical_Strike_Chance * ( 1 + Increased_Critical_Strike_Chance )  * ( 0.5 + Increased_Critical_Strike_Multiplier ) )
